import React from "react";
import { Container, Col, Tab, Nav, Row } from "react-bootstrap";
import "./AdminDashboard.css";

function AdminDashboard() {
  return (
    <Container mt-2>
      <Tab.Container>
        <Row>
          <Col sm={3}>
            <Nav variant="pills" className="flex-column">
              <Nav.Item eventKey="products">
                Products
              </Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Item eventKey="orders">
                Orders
              </Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Item eventKey="clients">
                Clients
              </Nav.Item>
            </Nav>
          </Col>
          <Col md={9}>
            <Tab.Content>
                Hello there,
            </Tab.Content>
          </Col>

        </Row>
      </Tab.Container>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default AdminDashboard;
